**19. What is the difference between rela ve, absolute, fixed, and s cky posi oning?** 
Rela ve posi oning keeps the element in the normal flow but allows small movements. 
Absolute posi oning removes the element from the flow rela ve to its nearest posi oned 
parent. Fixed posi oning locks the element to the screen window so it never moves during 
