**30. Explain accessibility in web development.** 
Accessibility means designing websites so that everyone can use them easily and comfortably. 
This includes people with disabili es, such as visual, hearing, or physical challenges. It involves 
using seman c HTML tags and adding text descrip ons to image files. Good accessibility allows 
